PROBLEM 1 — Google Trends is not a YouTube viral signal
--------------------------------------------------------
Many Google searches never become viral Shorts.
Examples: tax filing deadline, election polling, weather alerts.
These trend hugely on Google but perform terribly as Shorts topics.

CORRECT SOLUTION — Revised viral score formula:

