================================================================================
MISSING GAP 1 — NO CIRCUIT BREAKER (RETRY BUDGET)
================================================================================

PROBLEM
--------
Pipeline retries each video up to 3 times on quality failure.
No global retry budget exists.
3 consecutive videos failing all 3 attempts = 9 full render cycles.
This silently exhausts GitHub Actions runner minutes and API quota.

SOLUTION — Circuit breaker in main.py

Write logs/circuit_state.json. Track consecutive full failures.
Suspend pipeline after N=3 consecutive full failures.
Auto-reset after 24-hour cooldown.

Implementation:

    def check_circuit_breaker(threshold=3):
        state_path = LOG_DIR / "circuit_state.json"
        if state_path.exists():
            state = json.loads(state_path.read_text())
            fails = state.get("consecutive_full_failures", 0)
            if fails >= threshold:
                last_fail = state.get("last_failure_ts", 0)
                if time.time() - last_fail < 86400:  # 24hr cooldown
                    raise SystemExit(
                        f"Circuit open: {fails} consecutive failures. "
                        "Wait 24h or reset logs/circuit_state.json manually."
                    )

    def record_full_failure():
        state_path = LOG_DIR / "circuit_state.json"
        state = (json.loads(state_path.read_text())
                 if state_path.exists() else {})
        state["consecutive_full_failures"] = (
            state.get("consecutive_full_failures", 0) + 1
        )
        state["last_failure_ts"] = time.time()
        state_path.write_text(json.dumps(state, indent=2))

    def record_success():
        state_path = LOG_DIR / "circuit_state.json"
        state_path.write_text(
            json.dumps({"consecutive_full_failures": 0}, indent=2)
        )

Call check_circuit_breaker() at the start of main.py before Step 1.
Call record_full_failure() when all 3 retry attempts fail.
Call record_success() after successful upload in Step 13.

